extends layout

block content
  div(id='container', class='w-1/2 m-auto mt-6 mb-5 font-serif text-gray-300')
    h1(class='text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-black mb-2 text-gray-300')= title
    p Features are computed from a digitized image of a fine needle aspirate (FNA) of a breast mass.  They describe characteristics of the cell nuclei present in the image. A few of the images can be found at #[a(href='http://www.cs.wisc.edu/~street/images/', target='_blank') http://www.cs.wisc.edu/~street/images/].
    div(id='form-container', class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-7')
      each feature in features
        div(id='input')
          p #{feature}
          input(type='number', step=0.01, min=0, class='focus:border-none border-0 outline-0 border-b-[1px] border-gray-300 bg-gray-900')
    div(id='model_container')
      button(id='post_feature_values', class='border-[1px] border-gray-300 w-1/3 mr-[50px] hover:bg-gray-800', type='button', value='Submit', onclick='postFeatureValues()') Classify
      p(id='model_response', class='inline font-bold')